org.ow2.proactive.scheduler.common.util.logforwarder.appenders

Class AsyncAppenderWithStorage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.log4j.AppenderSkeleton
      • org.apache.log4j.AsyncAppender
        • org.ow2.proactive.scheduler.common.util.logforwarder.appenders.AsyncAppenderWithStorage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.log4j.Appender, org.apache.log4j.spi.AppenderAttachable, org.apache.log4j.spi.OptionHandler

    public class AsyncAppenderWithStorage
extends org.apache.log4j.AsyncAppender
    Class defines a log4j AsyncAppender that is able to store all appended event additionally to bufferize and send them to the added appenders.
    Since:
    ProActive Scheduling 0.9
